name: A Song of Hex and Jynx - #5 A Witch Must Embrace Herself
description: Sua might be seen as the weakest and the naive one among her sisters. Her gullible side had bring trouble to all of them before, that forced them to murder and ran away. Deep down she blamed herself for it, but she never showed it to her sisters. The thought of her emotion could bring doom to them again, made her decide to learn an ancient spell that could turn someone to be less emotionally driven. She practiced every time she got a chance while her sisters weren’t around. After so many attempts, she finally did it. She sensed the changed in her heart and mind. She felt lighter and something about it put her in a good mood. Not knowing an ancient spell, as hard as it was, could fabricate more than a witch could expect.
